flowchart TD
    Scheduled([Drop date minus 48h]) --> GenPreview[Generate preview - title and segments]
    GenPreview --> SendPreview[Send PREVIEW email]
    SendPreview --> Wait{Reply within 48h}
    Wait -->|silence| Produce[Enqueue produce_episode]
    Wait -->|perfect| Produce
    Wait -->|swap X for Y| Adjust[Update preview]
    Wait -->|skip| SkipCycle[Skip this cycle]
    Wait -->|pivot topic| Pivot[Update topic focus]
    Adjust --> Produce
    Pivot --> GenPreview
    Produce --> Ship[Episode ships on drop date]
    Ship --> NewEpisode[Send NEW EPISODE email]
    NewEpisode --> NextCycle([Schedule next cycle])
    SkipCycle --> NextCycle
